FBIS4-13411 "drnes076_l_94008" FBIS-NES-94-076 Daily Report 18 Apr 1994 ISRAEL Shin Bet Head Warns of Chaos After IDF Pullout Shin Bet Head Warns of Chaos After IDF Pullout TA1804073794 Tel Aviv YEDI'OT AHARONOT in Hebrew 18 Apr 94 p 7 TA1804073794 Tel Aviv YEDI'OT AHARONOT Hebrew BFN [Report by Smadar Peri and Shim'on Schiffer] [Excerpt] "Chaos is expected in the Gaza Strip immediately after the IDF [Israel Defense Forces] leaves the region and hands it over to the PLO." This assessment was made by the head of the Shin Bet at yesterday's cabinet session. The Shin Bet head anticipates that during the initial period after the IDF pullout, we will witness internecine massacres among the Palestinians. [passage omitted]
